fulltitle: Philip Agee: The CIA in the Post Cold War World
title: Philip Agee: The CIA in the Post Cold War World
_filename: _Philip Agee - The CIA in the Post Cold War World.webm
description: Philip Agee was a long-time CIA officer in Central and South America. He became disaffected with the methods and goals of the CIA, and blew the whistle in a book about the CIA called 'Inside the Company'.
